  <brief_title>L-citrulline and Metformin in Becker's Muscular Dystrophy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Study to Assess the Efficacy of L-Citrulline and Metformin in Adults With Becker's Muscular Dystrophy</official_title>
